<Layout title="Projects" description="Docker monorepo projects overview">
  <h1>Projects</h1>

  <p>The Docker monorepo contains the following projects:</p>

  <h2>Caddy with Cloudflare DNS</h2>
  <p>
    A high-performance web server with the Cloudflare DNS module integrated. Perfect for scenarios
    requiring automatic DNS management and high-performance request routing.
  </p>
  <p><a href="/projects/caddy/">View Caddy Documentation</a></p>

  <h2>Jenkins API</h2>
  <p>
    Jenkins container with pre-configured plugins and a Python test environment for testing the
    jenkinsapi library. Includes automated update checking for Jenkins versions and plugins.
  </p>
  <p><a href="/projects/jenkinsapi/">View Jenkins API Documentation</a></p>

  <h2>Ollama LLM Server</h2>
  <p>
    CPU-optimized LLM inference server providing an OpenAI-compatible API. Configurable for
    different memory and CPU constraints, perfect for local AI applications.
  </p>
  <p><a href="/projects/ollama/">View Ollama Documentation</a></p>

